
#### 2. `user_stories.md`
```markdown
# User Stories

1. As a user, I want to sign up for an account so that I can access the app.
2. As a user, I want to log in to my account so that I can use the app.
3. As a user, I want to see a home screen so that I can navigate the app.
4. As a user, I want to view detailed information about items so that I can make informed decisions.
5. As a user, I want to store data locally so that I can access it offline.
6. As a user, I want to integrate with an external API so that I can fetch data.
7. As a user, I want to access a settings menu so that I can customize the app.
8. As a user, I want to receive notifications so that I can stay updated.
9. As a user, I want to see error messages so that I can understand what went wrong.

